I followed theRospetto's Instructions from last year.   He is absolutely right - There are some instructions missing from that file, which once you put back [I used textedit, to open and then edit the file] works perfectly.   Thanks theRospetto!<br />
<br />
 brian<br />
&lt;!-- Sets a version number in Word 2013. --&gt;
<pre><code>  &lt;xsl:when test=&quot;b:XslVersion&quot;&gt;
    &lt;xsl:choose&gt;
      &lt;xsl:when test=&quot;msxsl:node-set($data)/general/version2013&quot;&gt;
        &lt;xsl:value-of select=&quot;msxsl:node-set($data)/general/version2013&quot;/&gt;
      &lt;/xsl:when&gt;
      &lt;xsl:otherwise&gt;
        &lt;!-- Fallback method : use a dummy version number of 1. --&gt;
        &lt;xsl:text&gt;1&lt;/xsl:text&gt;
      &lt;/xsl:otherwise&gt;
    &lt;/xsl:choose&gt;
  &lt;/xsl:when&gt;

  &lt;!-- Set the name of the style in Word 2013. --&gt;
  &lt;xsl:when test=&quot;b:StyleNameLocalized&quot;&gt;
    &lt;xsl:value-of select=&quot;msxsl:node-set($data)/general/stylename&quot;/&gt;
  &lt;/xsl:when&gt;</code></pre>
